{"id":17966,"date":"2022-12-31T04:21:39","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:21:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho-cr-v.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:21:39","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:21:39","slug":"honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho-cr-v","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho-cr-v\/","title":{"rendered":"Honda Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eb7ng 100% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 cho CR-V"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>H\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i \u00f4 t\u00f4 tung ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m 100% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 cho kh\u00e1ch mua CR-V, \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb 7\/12 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Honda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c, d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua m\u1eabu xe CR-V.  C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c thanh to\u00e1n 100% khi mua CR-V t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 7-31\/12 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ee9c 100% ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 (kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m VAT n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"CR-V tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Honda \u1edf TP.HCM.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho.png\" title=\"honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho-600x359.png 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/honda-viet-nam-tang-100-le-phi-truoc-ba-cho.png 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">CR-V tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Honda \u1edf TP.HCM.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u201cKh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i theo ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i kh\u00e1c theo th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eefa kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u00e3ng cho bi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">CR-V l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Honda t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  K\u1ebft th\u00fac 10 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y ghi nh\u1eadn doanh s\u1ed1 8.037 chi\u1ebfc, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.  \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u00e3ng xe Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft CR-V n\u1eb1m trong top xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd 3 n\u0103m nay, theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Focus2move.com, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean thu th\u1eadp v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 t\u00f4 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. .  .<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 CR-V hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, trang b\u1ecb g\u00f3i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e1i xe an to\u00e0n Honda Sensing, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u0103ng \u00e1p VTEC Turbo.  \u1ede n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee7a Honda c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i d\u00e0nh cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i linh ho\u1ea1t, v\u1edbi c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i 5+2.  Xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n t\u1eeb 998 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 1,138 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Ph\u1ea1m Trung<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i \u00f4 t\u00f4 tung ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m 100% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 cho kh\u00e1ch mua CR-V, \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb 7\/12 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Honda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c, d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua m\u1eabu [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16426,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17966"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17966"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17966\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16426"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17966"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.